title: First to the Finish
overview: First to the Finish - a New Docuseries Focused on the Relentless Pursuit of the MX-5 Cup Championship - Will Premiere March 25 on Prime VideoFrom Boardwalk Pictures, First to the Finish follows the journey of two female racers and one female team owner through the exhilarating 2024 Mazda MX-5 Cup Championship Season
